column5: There was a bad accident involving 6 trucks with 4 dead so far. They are saying that the highway east of 71 will be closed perhaps until sometime tomorrow. If you are headed to Dryden, you might want to go up 502 from the Fort.
can you get to fort frances from kenora still or is accedent before tun off down 17 cbprov
As I understand it, the road east of the Hi. 71 junction is closed. That means that you can get from Kenora to Ft. Frances.
